      'field2': value2,
      ...

    },

    {

    : 'field2': value3,
      'field3': value4,
      ...

    },

    ...

  \]

Output format::

: {

  : 'field1': [value1, None, ...],
    'field2': [value2, value3, ...],
    'field3': [None, value4, ...],
    ...

  }

If not all fields are present in every event None will be inserted instead.

